  <description type="morphology">Plants 5–10 dm. Aerial flowering stems not fistulose, 1–3(–4) dm, lanate to tomentose. Leaves usually basal, rarely sheathing; blade 2–3.5 × 1.5–2.5 cm, lanate abaxially, tomentose adaxially, margins plane. Inflorescences cymose, 30–100(–140) × 20–40 cm; branches lanate to tomentose. Involucres 1 per node, 3–4 mm, tomentose. Flowers 1.5–2 mm; perianth white, pubescent. 2n = 40.</description>
